snippet.title: Ace Attacker (Arcade) Japan Ver.
snippet.description:
Ace Attacker (エースアタッカー) is a volleyball game released for Sega System 16 arcade hardware. It is played from a top-down perspective.
Home computer conversions were planned to be produced by Activision, but were never released.
